is.ru.honn.rutube.domain

Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • is.ru.honn.rutube.domain.User

  • public class User
extends java.lang.Object
    Version:
    1.0, 28/09/16. This class contains a constructor for a video as well as get and set functions. The class also contains the addVideo function which adds a video to a list of videos.
    Author:
    Steinar Marinó Hilmarsson and Egill Gautur Steingrímsson.
